Doechii's song Anxiety, originally uploaded to YouTube in 2019, features her rapping and singing over Gotye and Kimbra's hit Somebody That I Used to Know. The track showcases Doechii's early experimental style, blending rap with alternative R&B. Initially a low-profile release, it gained renewed attention in 2025, prompting its official streaming debut. The song highlights Doechii's creativity and ability to reimagine a well-known melody into a deeply personal narrative.
